A masterfully forged Longsword that has an unexpectedly dull edge. This long blade was forged, and reinforced with magic to boost and protect the user. This fearsome weapon's appearance is almost at odds with its true purpose. Its appearance would make you believe it could tear apart a giant in one slash. This weapon was made under its owner's instructions to serve purely as a tool of deception. One focused on the sharp blade of the one in front of them won't be looking over their shoulder as the knife finds its mark in their back.
